    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion supports the conclusion that the device does not produce greater hemolysis than the predicate device under worst-case conditions.",
